{"tid":1739130,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"輸？咩黎架？想光復香港就入黎同我睇哂佢！！！！係無輸呢回事。","createTime":"2019-11-19T13:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T00:08:04.000Z","uid":120692,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"559fe34bd90d09168f52fe2f9bc75bb50dd88392","tid":1739130,"uid":120692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:05:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tye525dkfi8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ftye525dkfi8&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=99050e85\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tye525dkfi8</a><br />\n<br />\n神人Simon Sinek嘅演說，開字幕睇，有興趣買埋佢本書：The Infinite Game<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住，呢場民主運動係一個Infinite game，一千年一萬年只要有人嘅地方就要繼續，無得贏，奕即是說<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無得輸</span><br />\n<br />\n政府同狗隊以為呢場係Finite Game，佢地日日就係諗住點樣贏每一場仗，拉哂啲示威者，要人割蓆，證明自己係正義一方，妖魔化對手。呢啲全部都係Finite mindset。佢地連對手係邊個、諗乜都唔知，因為佢地連自己玩咩Game都仲未清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你睇返Video入面越戰個例子，美軍係幾乎贏哂每一場戰役，但係最後喺歷史上真正嘅勝利者係越南。<br />\n<br />\n你輸哂每場戰役又如何？中大，理大，乜都好，我地每一日就要思考，我地如何可以做得比昨天更好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足，明唔明白？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢場運動，無得輸。</span>"},{"pid":"8dfaf5fff51e27690e7a3ebfe71f9c8d864bdd0d","tid":1739130,"uid":120692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"05449b596a89f64abd3b6a20c4b66b24d079509c","tid":1739130,"uid":120692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:27:36.000Z","msg":"再推！"},{"pid":"21a164d07fcc86f9d0f5f6c7d244cd7514341afa","tid":1739130,"uid":202194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"559fe34bd90d09168f52fe2f9bc75bb50dd88392","tid":1739130,"uid":120692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:05:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tye525dkfi8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ftye525dkfi8&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=99050e85\" 